c: 17
v: 71
t: "Nabiyow! ugut ayrol sinam aytikumusak meesiisak ken taama elle tan kitaabal ken secnu wayna ayro keenih cus, tokkel le kitab migdah kah yantacawwu waa mari, toysa woo mari sinni kitab wallitak yakriye, ken taamah galtok tamri lafoyti berraaqimit yan tufulih gide keenik madaggoysimta"